{"tid":220451,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"囡囡想知點嚟 楊思琦：喺媽媽個肚度嚟","createTime":"2017-04-28T03:09:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:55:16.000Z","uid":3806,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb578e98a19a0ec30beecca07f88ce046da087af","tid":220451,"uid":3806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.celebrity.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/Cpxp6qksqjDmav9emWrDng--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20170427f153506.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.celebrity.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FCpxp6qksqjDmav9emWrDng--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20170427f153506.jpg&h=dd221b0e&s={SIZE}\" />【星島日報報道】邵仲衡、楊思琦為ViuTV 新劇《詭探》進行拍攝，楊思琦於劇中飾演心理醫生，飾演茅山術士的邵仲衡每次打敗強敵後，就會找楊思琦作心理輔導。<br />\n<br />\n楊思琦表示現實中亦似扮演心理醫生，多做聆聽者及解答5歲囡囡的疑問。問到囡囡可曾問及一些尷尬問題，如性教育？她說：「我答佢喺媽媽個肚度嚟，囡囡有學游水，我都會教佢除咗媽媽同婆婆，唔好畀其他人掂身體。」另外，邵仲衡自言近期跟幾位香港小姐出身的靚女合作：「我發覺佢哋有共通點，都係好專業，keep得好fit，個人好有紀律同自制能力。」"},{"pid":"039ba7b73c1548c41e199b49bc973201b7a15479","tid":220451,"uid":3806,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:11:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04/131014_392b729f79ef74952166e21b118354f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F04%2F131014_392b729f79ef74952166e21b118354f0.jpg&h=4e10eb27&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"343b98669eb0024d692b7d1dd95b5b8fc619bd12","tid":220451,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:13:13.000Z","msg":"阿女 你老母係支那肉便器 仲臭過公廁阿"},{"pid":"93eb124d749054402c6f37833b0ad55341159242","tid":220451,"uid":107539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T03:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/04